          <li><a href={url("/case-studies/china-backbone")}>Beijing–Shanghai backbone</a> — the QKD-only contrast.</li>
          <li><a href={url("/case-studies/knaut-boston")}>Knaut Boston-metro demo</a> — entanglement-based, with quantum memories.</li>
          <li><a href={url("/companies/qubitekk")}>Qubitekk vendor dossier</a> — the entangled-photon-source hardware supplier (acquired by IonQ, 2024–25).</li>
          <li><a href={url("/companies/ionq")}>IonQ vendor dossier</a> — the 2025 compute partner.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

    </Stack>
